window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A broken curse, fractured relationships, and the return of an old enemy....</b></p> <p>A brief moment of victory is overshadowed by the resurgence of an old foe seeking Bryn's help. But sudden losses have shattered Bryn, and she must take solace in the men who haven't abandoned her. </p> <p>Her hope to start a new life with her remaining lovers is dashed when a dangerous supernatural drug makes its way to the streets. She can't begin again when the poison that ruined her life is left unchecked to destroy more families. </p> <p>But stopping the spread will force Bryn to make uneasy alliances-and lie to the men she loves. Her crusade could cost more than she's willing to pay, but backing down will spell disaster for supernaturals and non-magical people alike. Bryn must choose between her own happiness and the fate of the world.</p> <p><i>Contains mature themes.</i></p>"; 
